BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ kilogram} = 1000 \text{ grams} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$kg1] \text{ kilograms} = ``] [__________]{$g1} [`` \text{ grams} ``]

b. [`` [$g2] \text{ grams} = ``] [__________]{$kg2} [`` \text{ kilograms} ``]

END_PGML


